Use the structure below to complete the requirements:
The div width and height are 400px.
Set the image at the beginning of the assignments as the background of the element.
In Shape 1, make the background not repeat at all.
In Shape 2, make the background repeat vertically only.
In Shape 3, make the background repeat horizontally only.
In Shape 4, make the background repeat both vertically and horizontally.

..................................................................................
